metadata.name: Your feelings -  a drop of invisible power
metadata.description:
NFT for business. This NFT is a license to use this artwork for textile prints. By purchasing this NFT, you get two fragments of a complete picture for printing on fabric. 
All rights to use the NFT pass into full ownership of the buyer immediately after the purchase of the NFT, along with permission for commercial use.
The NFT will be sending to the buyer directly.

https://annasiberian.com

Created by Anna Lalaian
